 cost curves are labeled S R A T C sub 1 through S R A T C sub 5. Each S R A T C curve touches the L R A T C curve at a point. Curve S R A T C sub 1 touches curve L R A T C directly above quantity Q sub 1. Curve S R A T C sub 2 touches curve L R A T C directly above quantity Q sub 2. Curve S R A T C sub 3 touches curve L R A T C directly above quantity Q sub 3. Curve S R A T C sub 4 touches curve L R A T C directly above quantity Q sub 4. Curve S R A T C sub 5 touches curve L R A T C directly above quantity Q sub 5.\" height=\"255\" src=\"https://assets.learnosity.com/organisations/537/VH926494.g05.png\" width=\"450\" /></div>\n</div>\n"}],"choicesHtml":["<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"S R A T C sub 1\"><math alttext=\"S R A T C sub 1\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><msub><mrow><mtext>SRATC</mtext></mrow><mrow><mn>1</mn></mrow></msub></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"S R A T C sub 2\"><math alttext=\"S R A T C sub 2\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><msub><mrow><mtext>SRATC</mtext></mrow><mrow><mn>2</mn></mrow></msub></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"S R A T C sub 3\"><math alttext=\"S R A T C sub 3\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><msub><mrow><mtext>SRATC</mtext></mrow><mrow><mn>3</mn></mrow></msub></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"S R A T C sub 4\"><math alttext=\"S R A T C sub 4\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><msub><mrow><mtext>SRATC</mtext></mrow><mrow><mn>4</mn></mrow></msub></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"S R A T C sub 5\"><math alttext=\"S R A T C sub 5\" display